Title: FITClub
Description: FITClub is platform fighting arcade game for 2 to 4 players. Enemies are controlled by AI. The goal is to force enemies down into the water or lava and keep safe from their attacks. You collect items to temporarily change your abilities. Multiplayer between more phones is coming soon.
